data.description: Beautifully updated home with gorgeous hardwood flooring in Living room and hallway. Granite countertops, updated bathrooms and kitchen, stainelss allpliances and all appliances stay including washer and dryer! The big open living room has a nice gas log fireplace - no flickering electric lights here - this is the real deal! Check it out today!
